						<div class="postbody">So here's how Alisha's Adventure sounds like with an FM synth main instrument, with these settings:<br /><br />carrier frequency = #$04<br />modulation frequency = #$08<br />modulation amplitude = #$FF<br /><br />Not too interesting though.  I tried sliding the modulation amplitude and frequency up and down, neither sounded interesting enough to post.  Maybe if I had a 3rd oscillator, I could do more interesting timbre changes.</div>

					
